---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Customers" description="Teams running HelixGitpx in production.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Customers</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">
      Early customer logos, case studies, and testimonials land here after
      GA. To be listed, email <a href="mailto:hello@helixgitpx.io" class="text-primary hover:underline">hello@helixgitpx.io</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">Beta cohort · 2026</div>
      <div class="mt-3 text-2xl font-semibold">Private beta in progress</div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Case studies publish as beta customers complete 30 days of stable production.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded bg-primary px-5 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-blue-700">Get your team on the list</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
